title: Version 1.0.4 of the app now includes:
message:
Version 1.0.4 of the app now includes:
- enter key in password field performs login function
- touch observed date field launches DatePicker to choose date
- touch observed time field launches TimePicker to choose time
- precip field only accepts decimal numbers and T with the numeric keypad shown by default
- enter key in notes field hides the soft keyboard
- enter key in precip field hides the soft keyboard
- soft keyboard hidden by default in precip report form
